00:00:33,600 --> 00:00:36,280
♫  Enduring the trials of life and death  ♫

4
00:00:36,280 --> 00:00:40,600
♫  As I gaze into the dark night  ♫

5
00:00:41,510 --> 00:00:44,280
♫  My spirit has not been broken  ♫

6
00:00:44,280 --> 00:00:46,920
♫  And unleash this passion  ♫

7
00:00:46,920 --> 00:00:51,840
♫  My spirit will only grow stronger  ♫

8
00:00:51,840 --> 00:00:54,860
♫  Splitting mountains and parting seas  ♫

9
00:00:54,860 --> 00:00:57,500
♫  Answering the sword's call and entering the Martial World  ♫

10
00:00:57,500 --> 00:01:02,540
♫  I'm the chosen one, fate in this turbulent world  ♫

11
00:01:02,540 --> 00:01:05,440
♫  Keeping my distance from the world  ♫

12
00:01:05,440 --> 00:01:08,220
♫  Who can understand my loneliness?  ♫

13
00:01:08,220 --> 00:01:11,920
♫  A single thought, gazing down  ♫

14
00:01:11,920 --> 00:01:14,640
♫  With swords drawn, frost flies through the air  ♫

15
00:01:14,640 --> 00:01:17,280
♫  With faith that conquers the world with one strike  ♫

16
00:01:17,280 --> 00:01:22,520
♫  Soaring through the sky, the sword reigns everywhere  ♫

17
00:01:22,520 --> 00:01:25,240
♫  Breaking through the waves, dancing drunkenly everywhere  ♫

18
00:01:25,240 --> 00:01:27,860
♫  Protecting the people, no matter the cost  ♫

19
00:01:27,860 --> 00:01:32,220
♫  Atop the peak, you and I shall battle all out  ♫

20
00:01:32,220 --> 00:01:34,600

21
00:01:40,110 --> 00:01:43,720

22
00:01:43,720 --> 00:01:48,420

23
00:01:49,240 --> 00:01:52,020

24
00:01:56,860 --> 00:02:02,660
Right now, Prince Jingyu's Mansion and the Shadow Sect have become a family.

25
00:02:02,660 --> 00:02:05,820
This really is frustrating.

26
00:02:07,680 --> 00:02:12,220
Your Highness, the carriage sent by Prince Jingyu's Mansion has been waiting outside for some time.

27
00:02:12,220 --> 00:02:15,820
- Your Highness, should we... 
 - I'm not going.

28
00:02:15,860 --> 00:02:17,900
Tell them I have a headache.

29
00:02:17,900 --> 00:02:20,900
- Your Highness, please wait. 
 - For what?

30
00:02:20,900 --> 00:02:24,480
I won't show any respect for Prince Jingyu. What can he do about it?

31
00:02:24,480 --> 00:02:29,200
Complain about me in front of Imperial Father? Tell them to get lost.

32
00:02:31,740 --> 00:02:35,660
It's not about the wedding banquet. Someone is charging toward Prince Jingyu's Mansion.

33
00:02:35,660 --> 00:02:38,020
Judging from their actions, they're trying to steal the bride.

34
00:02:38,020 --> 00:02:42,620
The Shadow Sect has already sent Shadow Guards to stop them, but they seem to have failed.

35
00:02:42,620 --> 00:02:45,580
What did you say? They're trying to steal the bride?

36
00:02:45,580 --> 00:02:47,180
That's right.

37
00:02:49,060 --> 00:02:51,720
Who is it? Who's stealing the bride?

38
00:02:52,740 --> 00:02:57,340
Ye Dingzhi. Also known as Ye Yun.

39
00:03:02,140 --> 00:03:07,980
Are you sure he's here to steal the bride and not here to... kill me?

40
00:03:07,980 --> 00:03:10,440
He's here to steal the bride.

41
00:03:10,440 --> 00:03:14,680
Ye Dingzhi and Yi Wenjun, the daughter of the Shadow Sect's leader, have been engaged since young.

42
00:03:14,680 --> 00:03:18,380
Therefore, his attempt at stealing the bride isn't without merit.

43
00:03:23,820 --> 00:03:26,780
He could reach Prince Jingyu's Mansion all by himself?

44
00:03:26,780 --> 00:03:29,160
Initially, he couldn't, but someone's helping him.

45
00:03:29,160 --> 00:03:32,000
- Who is it? 
 - A spear wielder.

46
00:03:32,000 --> 00:03:36,140
It's the man we saw during the drinking contest at Diaolou Tavern.

47
00:03:36,140 --> 00:03:40,340
As for the other guy, judging by his techniques, he should be a member of the Shadow Sect.

48
00:03:40,340 --> 00:03:43,460
There's one more. He has a special sword.

49
00:03:43,460 --> 00:03:46,620
It resembles the sword wielded by Mister Li's last disciple, Baili Dongjun.

50
00:03:46,620 --> 00:03:49,100
You mean the young master of Marquis Zhenxi's Mansion?

51
00:03:49,100 --> 00:03:50,820
Indeed.

52
00:03:57,540 --> 00:04:00,140
Marquis Zhenxi's Mansion, huh?

53
00:04:00,140 --> 00:04:04,500
His father is establishing an alliance with us, while his son is going against us.

54
00:04:04,500 --> 00:04:07,840
This is interesting. Let's go.

55
00:04:07,840 --> 00:04:09,940
Your Highness, where are you heading?

56
00:04:09,940 --> 00:04:14,380
Naturally, it's Prince Jingyu's Mansion. We have a show to catch.

57
00:04:14,380 --> 00:04:16,200
Your Highness, please wait.

58
00:04:19,800 --> 00:04:25,360
Since we're doomed either way, let's just observe the situation for now.

59
00:04:44,100 --> 00:04:48,900
Qingyang, I'm very disappointed in you.

60
00:04:48,900 --> 00:04:50,600
Master.

61
00:04:52,160 --> 00:04:54,740
I'm very disappointed in you as well.

62
00:04:56,900 --> 00:05:01,340
Will you draw your sword against me today?

63
00:05:03,540 --> 00:05:05,540
I've always wondered

64
00:05:06,540 --> 00:05:09,540
whether I would draw my sword against you one day, Master.

65
00:05:11,020 --> 00:05:17,020
Maybe when the day arrived, I would no longer fear you.

66
00:05:17,660 --> 00:05:22,580
I would be brave enough to pursue the things I like.

67
00:05:22,580 --> 00:05:29,620
Excellent. I would've been relieved to hear that if the circumstances were otherwise.

68
00:05:29,620 --> 00:05:31,700
Draw your sword.

69
00:05:31,700 --> 00:05:35,360
Sorry for the offense, Master.

70
00:05:50,120 --> 00:05:54,720
It seems I've overestimated myself. I used up too much energy back there.

71
00:05:54,720 --> 00:05:59,440
I'm here. My powers have increased considerably after mastering the Sword of Longing.

72
00:05:59,440 --> 00:06:03,300
Not even my senior can stop me now.

73
00:06:03,300 --> 00:06:06,800
- Which senior were you referring to? 
 - None of them...

74
00:06:06,800 --> 00:06:08,780
What are you doing here?

75
00:06:10,900 --> 00:06:14,400
- Heir Apparent. 
 - I'll take them both with me.

76
00:06:14,400 --> 00:06:17,540
They won't go to Prince Jingyu's Mansion. You can head back.

77
00:06:17,540 --> 00:06:20,980
Who are you to order us around?

78
00:06:20,980 --> 00:06:24,980
Since you're this arrogant while standing, lie down then.

79
00:06:28,620 --> 00:06:30,860
Do you know what you're doing right now?

80
00:06:30,860 --> 00:06:32,800
Of course.

81
00:06:34,920 --> 00:06:39,680
I'm here to help Brother Yun. As long as Brother Yun is still alive, his engagement with Wenjun is valid.

82
00:06:39,680 --> 00:06:41,820
Moreover, they love each other. They should be together.

83
00:06:41,820 --> 00:06:44,100
You cannot stop me today.

84
00:06:44,960 --> 00:06:47,320
Give it a try, then.

85
00:06:47,320 --> 00:06:50,540
- Senior Lei, do you wish to give it a try as well? 
 - You misunderstood me.

86
00:06:50,540 --> 00:06:54,700
This is your family affair. It's none of my business. You guys can go ahead.

87
00:06:54,700 --> 00:06:58,380
Heir Apparent, please teach him a lesson on my behalf.

88
00:06:58,380 --> 00:07:01,020
Heir Apparent, sorry for the offense!

89
00:07:04,620 --> 00:07:07,775

90
00:07:13,740 --> 00:07:19,520
Dingzhi, do you want to come up here and enjoy a drink with me?

91
00:07:21,780 --> 00:07:23,420
I'm in a hurry.

92
00:07:23,420 --> 00:07:28,460
I'm in a hurry, too. I have a banquet to attend in the front yard.

93
00:07:29,840 --> 00:07:33,460
We still have time for a drink, though.

94
00:07:35,660 --> 00:07:38,570

95
00:07:51,260 --> 00:07:55,340
 The bride taking her own life during the wedding banquet,

96
00:07:55,340 --> 00:08:03,520
 this should embarrass a conceited person like Xiao Ruojin more than anything.

97
00:08:11,940 --> 00:08:15,020
Young Lady, it's time.

98
00:08:15,020 --> 00:08:18,020
Have you detected any movement out there?

99
00:08:18,020 --> 00:08:20,020
They've already rung the gong.

100
00:08:20,020 --> 00:08:21,900
That's not what I'm asking.

101
00:08:21,900 --> 00:08:26,060
I mean, did the wedding proceed smoothly?

102
00:08:26,060 --> 00:08:30,440
Everything is proceeding smoothly. Now, we just need to send you to the hall.

103
00:08:39,160 --> 00:08:44,080
 Six months. Wait six months for me. I'll be back.

104
00:09:03,020 --> 00:09:06,180
Back then, I had great hopes for you.

105
00:09:06,180 --> 00:09:11,440
I thought you would become my junior as well.

106
00:09:12,980 --> 00:09:16,220
We almost became disciples of the same master.

107
00:09:16,220 --> 00:09:18,700
I think this toast is enough.

108
00:09:20,260 --> 00:09:24,160
You're the descendant of General Ye. I admire you.

109
00:09:24,160 --> 00:09:26,900
If it's possible,

110
00:09:26,900 --> 00:09:31,540
Dingzhi, you should stop here. Stop fighting.

111
00:09:31,540 --> 00:09:36,080
But there's a lady waiting for me inside. I don't want to disappoint her.

112
00:09:41,900 --> 00:09:44,520
You're no match for me.

113
00:09:44,520 --> 00:09:49,600
Even so... we won't know until we fight.

114
00:09:55,180 --> 00:09:59,820
Haoque Sword, ranked eighth out of the top ten in Record of Famous Swords.

115
00:09:59,820 --> 00:10:03,060
It's known as The Sword of Righteousness.

116
00:10:03,060 --> 00:10:08,520
But, Little Master, do you think your action today is worthy of its title?

117
00:10:09,220 --> 00:10:14,840
Power? The bigger picture? Are those truly more important than her will?

118
00:10:17,940 --> 00:10:19,580
Sorry for this.

119
00:10:41,980 --> 00:10:45,440
You're much stronger than you were six months ago.

120
00:10:45,440 --> 00:10:50,660
It's because I spent the past six months preparing for this day alone.

121
00:10:51,940 --> 00:10:54,660
- You learned the Demon Deity Sword Techniques? 
 - So what if I did?

122
00:10:54,660 --> 00:10:57,400
Learning that technique will cause great stress to one's body.

123
00:10:57,400 --> 00:11:00,060
You're still young. You shouldn't have learned that.

124
00:11:00,060 --> 00:11:03,900
You shouldn't repeat your master's mistake.

125
00:11:03,900 --> 00:11:09,600
As long as I win today, then it won't have been a mistake. It's over!

126
00:11:28,140 --> 00:11:30,780
You've underestimated me.

127
00:11:30,780 --> 00:11:35,020
That's the Xiao Family's Lieguo Sword Technique.

128
00:11:35,820 --> 00:11:38,740
You thought you could win.

129
00:11:38,740 --> 00:11:44,340
Since you learned the Demon Deity Sword Techniques, that proves you know you can't win.

130
00:11:53,100 --> 00:11:56,020
You knew that you couldn't win.

131
00:11:56,020 --> 00:12:00,060
That's why you're risking everything you have to learn this move.

132
00:12:00,060 --> 00:12:06,630
The Rain Demon could never beat Mister Li, just like you can never beat me.

133
00:12:06,630 --> 00:12:12,010
Dingzhi, leave or die.

134
00:12:25,540 --> 00:12:29,440
How dare you talk back to your father when this is all you have?

135
00:12:29,440 --> 00:12:32,820
Baili Chengfeng! You're not the one getting married here.

136
00:12:32,820 --> 00:12:34,580
Why are you putting so much effort into this?

137
00:12:34,580 --> 00:12:38,400
I just want to let you know that when youngsters like you try to go against adults,

138
00:12:38,400 --> 00:12:43,540
they need to think about whether they're strong enough to overcome the hurdle.

139
00:12:43,540 --> 00:12:46,920
If they're not strong enough, they can still afford to wait.

140
00:12:50,620 --> 00:12:52,680
Still not enough.

141
00:13:05,620 --> 00:13:08,260
 I don't wish to miss out on that sword technique.

142
00:13:09,980 --> 00:13:13,860
 I don't wish to regret that I didn't get to see that sword technique today

143
00:13:13,860 --> 00:13:18,220
 after losing everything I have.

144
00:13:20,180 --> 00:13:24,260
 It's pointless even if you see it.

145
00:13:24,920 --> 00:13:30,540
 It's just like how Rain Demon can never defeat Li Changsheng.

146
00:13:31,460 --> 00:13:33,480
That's right.

147
00:13:34,580 --> 00:13:36,940
I thought I couldn't win.

148
00:13:36,940 --> 00:13:39,820
That's why I'm risking everything I have.

149
00:13:39,820 --> 00:13:42,620
But I'm different from Master.

150
00:13:43,260 --> 00:13:48,140
If he can't win, he'll wait for his next chance.

151
00:13:48,140 --> 00:13:50,700
This is my only chance.

152
00:13:50,700 --> 00:13:55,420
If I can't win, I will continue to think of other solutions.

153
00:13:55,420 --> 00:13:59,020
I'll think of solutions and keep on winning!

154
00:14:01,220 --> 00:14:07,900
Immovable Lord Technique, now!

155
00:14:14,820 --> 00:14:16,940
If I keep waiting,

156
00:14:16,940 --> 00:14:21,600
the girl he loves will belong to someone else.

157
00:14:23,380 --> 00:14:26,680
I will never let them achieve their dirty goals.

158
00:14:26,680 --> 00:14:30,740
Dongjun, if she were the girl you like,

159
00:14:30,740 --> 00:14:34,720
I would resist the world with you, even if everyone were against us.

160
00:14:34,720 --> 00:14:36,920
I'd beat them up until they agreed with you.

161
00:14:36,920 --> 00:14:39,640
It's a shame that she's not.

162
00:14:39,640 --> 00:14:41,820
You're here to steal a bride on a stranger's behalf.

163
00:14:41,820 --> 00:14:43,840
He's not a stranger!

164
00:14:46,460 --> 00:14:48,500
He's Brother Yun.

165
00:14:49,980 --> 00:14:54,180
You once promised me that you would protect the Shadow Sect.

166
00:14:54,180 --> 00:14:58,700
But Junior Sister shouldn't be the sect's sacrificial lamb!

167
00:15:04,340 --> 00:15:06,840
Don't do it! You've already used Demon Deity Sword Techniques.

168
00:15:06,840 --> 00:15:11,720
If you use Immovable Lord Technique now and activate both sinister skills, you'll die at any time!

169
00:15:11,720 --> 00:15:14,180
There's no way back now.

170
00:15:14,180 --> 00:15:18,040
Anyway, I won't leave. At most, I'll just die here.

171
00:15:18,040 --> 00:15:21,260
Ye Dingzhi, why are you putting yourself through this?

172
00:15:21,260 --> 00:15:27,320
Rumor has it that Prince Langya, Xiao Ruofeng, is open-minded and righteous.

173
00:15:27,320 --> 00:15:30,440
He's the most magnanimous person among the princes.

174
00:15:30,440 --> 00:15:35,400
"Even with such magnanimity, you still can't tolerate the love between two people?

175
00:15:35,400 --> 00:15:38,620
This wedding is a marriage alliance between the Shadow Sect and Prince Jingyu’s Mansion.

176
00:15:38,620 --> 00:15:40,380
I can't just...

177
00:15:45,880 --> 00:15:50,480
If Prince Qing gains influence, the world will be in turmoil.

178
00:15:50,480 --> 00:15:54,560
So, for the sake of the world,

179
00:15:54,560 --> 00:15:57,940
you'll sacrifice the relationship of a loving couple, right?

180
00:15:57,940 --> 00:16:04,080
Just like how my family was slain to achieve world peace, right?!

181
00:16:04,900 --> 00:16:07,740
- Sorry about this. 
 - Die!

182
00:16:11,060 --> 00:16:13,840
The auspicious hour is nearing.

183
00:16:15,420 --> 00:16:21,210
Young Lady, if you don't move now, when the steward gets angry, I'll be...

184
00:16:23,740 --> 00:16:25,940
I wish to wait a little longer.

185
00:16:25,940 --> 00:16:29,980
Young Lady, what are you waiting for?

186
00:16:32,740 --> 00:16:34,540
What's your name?

187
00:16:34,540 --> 00:16:36,660
My name is Xiao Die.

188
00:16:36,660 --> 00:16:39,400
Can you sing?

189
00:16:39,400 --> 00:16:41,360
I can.

190
00:16:41,820 --> 00:16:49,430
Do you know how to sing the most popular song in Tianqi City, "Butterfly Lovers"?

191
00:16:55,540 --> 00:17:02,280
♪  Green willows and mist hasten the end of spring  ♪

192
00:17:02,280 --> 00:17:06,200
♪  The fog is light and cold  ♪

193
00:17:06,200 --> 00:17:10,980
♪  The swallows fly off in pairs  ♪

194
00:17:10,980 --> 00:17:17,540
♫  The bright moon doesn't understand the bitterness of parting  ♫

195
00:17:17,540 --> 00:17:26,400
♫  Its slanting rays shine through the red door until dawn  ♫

196
00:17:26,400 --> 00:17:33,300
♫  The west wind withered the green trees last night  ♫

197
00:17:33,300 --> 00:17:36,340
♫  Alone, climbing the high tower  ♫

198
00:17:36,340 --> 00:17:38,300
It's your win.

199
00:17:42,260 --> 00:17:44,520
Ye Dingzhi!

200
00:17:45,460 --> 00:17:49,220
Even if you defeat me, you won't be able to leave Tianqi.

201
00:17:49,220 --> 00:17:52,940
If you go berserk, you'll become wasted for the rest of your life!

202
00:17:52,940 --> 00:17:54,820
Give up!

203
00:17:54,820 --> 00:17:57,080
"Give up"?

204
00:17:59,220 --> 00:18:02,880
I no longer wish to give up on anything.

205
00:18:02,880 --> 00:18:05,560
I will never give up.

206
00:18:05,560 --> 00:18:09,620
I won't stop until I die!

207
00:18:09,620 --> 00:18:13,660
Ye Dingzhi. Ye Dingzhi!

208
00:18:13,660 --> 00:18:15,900
 The auspicious hour has arrived!

209
00:18:15,900 --> 00:18:20,660
 Play the music. Welcome the newlyweds.

210
00:18:36,060 --> 00:18:39,400
 This is bad. He has lost his mind.

211
00:18:51,740 --> 00:18:53,860
I won.

212
00:19:12,340 --> 00:19:14,300
I...

213
00:19:25,700 --> 00:19:27,840
I won...

214
00:19:36,300 --> 00:19:39,660
Young Lady, we're just waiting for you.

215
00:19:41,500 --> 00:19:44,380
Is there still no movement outside the residence?

216
00:19:45,820 --> 00:19:48,040
Nothing's changed.

217
00:19:48,040 --> 00:19:51,640
E-Everything is fine.

218
00:19:54,980 --> 00:19:56,860
All right, then.

219
00:20:03,020 --> 00:20:04,960
Let's not wait any longer.

220
00:20:39,660 --> 00:20:42,440
You should leave together with him. Forget your dumb ideas.

221
00:20:42,440 --> 00:20:46,400
You can't defeat me, even after ten years.

222
00:20:47,260 --> 00:20:51,520
But if Baili Dongjun finds out that I surrender before fighting you,

223
00:20:51,520 --> 00:20:54,340
he'll mock me for the next ten years.

224
00:20:55,340 --> 00:20:57,160
What are you going to do, then?

225
00:20:57,160 --> 00:20:58,620
You want to be like him?

226
00:20:58,620 --> 00:21:00,900
My master taught me some new spear techniques.

227
00:21:00,900 --> 00:21:02,740
I wish to try them on you.

228
00:21:06,340 --> 00:21:09,800
Dragon Transformation!

229
00:21:10,740 --> 00:21:12,700
Stop your transformation.

230
00:21:16,260 --> 00:21:18,020
Youngsters like you all talk too much.

231
00:21:18,020 --> 00:21:20,620
Still mainly inexperienced.

232
00:21:29,780 --> 00:21:33,100
Kill me! Kill me!

233
00:21:34,660 --> 00:21:37,320
You want to die now?

234
00:21:37,320 --> 00:21:43,040
Don't you wish to come back, defeat me, and escape with Wenjun in the future?

235
00:21:43,040 --> 00:21:47,740
To lose and die is simply the mindset of a weakling.

236
00:21:47,740 --> 00:21:51,680
And you said you wanted to be the top martial artist?

237
00:21:51,680 --> 00:21:55,500
There's no second chance when it comes to this.

238
00:21:55,500 --> 00:21:59,640
You're indeed the strongest disciple the Shadow Sect has had in the last several decades.

239
00:21:59,640 --> 00:22:02,840
You were stronger than me when I was young.

240
00:22:02,840 --> 00:22:05,160
But that's not enough.

241
00:22:05,160 --> 00:22:08,160
You have to become stronger.

242
00:22:19,680 --> 00:22:21,100
Take him away.

243
00:22:21,100 --> 00:22:26,020
No one can release him without my orders.

244
00:22:27,900 --> 00:22:31,220
Master!

245
00:22:44,060 --> 00:22:46,140
This brat.

246
00:22:46,140 --> 00:22:49,680
He's actually this powerful at this age.

247
00:22:49,680 --> 00:22:54,740
Maybe there's a chance for him to be the top martial artist after all.

248
00:22:56,380 --> 00:23:00,060
Xiaoying, take him away.

249
00:23:00,060 --> 00:23:01,760
Put him in a carriage.

250
00:23:01,760 --> 00:23:04,475
Do not let anyone see him.

251
00:23:04,475 --> 00:23:07,925

252
00:23:10,860 --> 00:23:12,360
You're seriously wounded.

253
00:23:12,360 --> 00:23:14,760
Are you still going to attend the wedding?

254
00:23:19,120 --> 00:23:20,960
I have to go.

255
00:23:21,980 --> 00:23:24,320
I must go.

256
00:23:25,220 --> 00:23:27,980
This wedding...

257
00:23:27,980 --> 00:23:33,000
 looks perfectly normal in every aspect.

258
00:23:33,000 --> 00:23:38,930
 It's so normal, as if nothing else had happened.

259
00:24:13,460 --> 00:24:15,840
Ruofeng, are you all right?

260
00:24:15,840 --> 00:24:18,700
Brother, I'm fine.

261
00:24:18,700 --> 00:24:21,340
You should receive your bride.

262
00:24:39,860 --> 00:24:45,300
 During the 16th year of Taihe's era, Prince Jingyu, Xiao Ruojin, took Yi as his secondary consort.

263
00:24:45,300 --> 00:24:47,740
 The Emperor was very pleased.

264
00:24:47,740 --> 00:24:50,580
 Emperor Tai'an valued her virtuous nature

265
00:24:50,580 --> 00:24:53,140
 and appreciated her father's contribution to the state,

266
00:24:53,140 --> 00:24:57,080
 so specially promoted her to principal consort, alongside the current consort.

267
00:25:08,580 --> 00:25:10,180
 She's going to take her own life.

268
00:25:10,180 --> 00:25:14,660
 Everything will be over now.

269
00:25:56,960 --> 00:26:01,420
 I was just one step away.

