275
00:26:19,398 --> 00:26:23,158
♫  I will never see the face of my old friend again  ♫

276
00:26:24,100 --> 00:26:26,320
Was that Brother Yun?

277
00:26:26,320 --> 00:26:29,420
Dongjun, don't worry.

278
00:26:29,420 --> 00:26:33,404
Prince Langya said he would ensure his safety.

279
00:26:36,318 --> 00:26:37,536

280
00:26:37,536 --> 00:26:41,878
♫  Allow me to see you one more time before I leave  ♫

281
00:26:41,878 --> 00:26:43,738
♫  Hoping  ♫

282
00:26:43,738 --> 00:26:47,670
♫  Hoping that my dreams will still be fulfilled  ♫

283
00:26:48,898 --> 00:26:52,260
 Wait six months for me. I'll be back.

284
00:26:52,260 --> 00:26:55,240
 If you wish to try the beef there, you can visit the plains.

285
00:26:55,240 --> 00:26:58,200
 If you wish to pray to the Buddha statues, you can head to the Buddhist states.

286
00:26:58,200 --> 00:27:01,220
 If you wish to try the herbal tea of Nanjue, you can head to Nanjue.

287
00:27:01,220 --> 00:27:04,580
 If you want to travel east by boat, you can head to the largest port in the east

288
00:27:04,580 --> 00:27:06,600
 and set sail.

289
00:27:06,600 --> 00:27:08,180
 The world is vast.

290
00:27:08,180 --> 00:27:10,569
 Tianqi isn't the only place in the world.

291
00:27:11,140 --> 00:27:12,890
 The weather today is great.

292
00:27:12,890 --> 00:27:14,770
 It's appropriate for a trip.

293
00:27:15,380 --> 00:27:19,259
 Especially a long trip that we'll never return from.

294
00:27:22,198 --> 00:27:25,998
♫  By the window  ♫

295
00:27:35,001 --> 00:27:38,300
♫  If the world were destroyed at my fingertips  ♫

296
00:27:38,300 --> 00:27:40,260
Stay put.

297
00:27:42,200 --> 00:27:44,240
♫  ... nothing left to care about  ♫

298
00:27:44,240 --> 00:27:46,501
 Wenjun...

299
00:27:46,501 --> 00:27:50,741
♫  Spring and Autumn continue to pass   ♫

300
00:27:50,741 --> 00:27:53,421
♫  Not recognizing  ♫

301
00:27:53,421 --> 00:27:56,781
♫  Old faces   ♫

302
00:27:56,781 --> 00:28:02,201
♫  The heart had dreams that were not yet fulfilled   ♫

303
00:28:02,201 --> 00:28:04,420
♫  Hearts filled with anguish  ♫

304
00:28:04,420 --> 00:28:07,600
That was him, right?

305
00:28:10,800 --> 00:28:14,830
I promise you. I'll ensure his safety.

306
00:28:16,301 --> 00:28:17,961
♫  Hoping  ♫

307
00:28:17,961 --> 00:28:21,940
♫  Hoping that my dreams will still be fulfilled  ♫

308
00:28:21,940 --> 00:28:24,080
♫  Memories seep into my mind  ♫

309
00:28:24,080 --> 00:28:28,525
Sister-in-law, your veil was blown away.

310
00:28:29,201 --> 00:28:33,201
♫  Alas, sighing at a fate that is so sorrowful  ♫

311
00:28:33,201 --> 00:28:39,041
♫  Because of you, the gratitude and grievances stir yet remain unsaid  ♫

312
00:28:39,041 --> 00:28:40,941
♫  Longing  ♫

