00:28:42,140 --> 00:28:44,160
Let's perform the rites.

314
00:28:44,740 --> 00:28:48,041
♫  Balancing on a thin line  ♫

315
00:28:48,041 --> 00:28:50,701
Bow to Heaven and Earth!

316
00:28:51,881 --> 00:28:55,821
♫  Is that from now on you're alone in this world  ♫

317
00:28:55,821 --> 00:28:58,921
♫  By the window  ♫

318
00:28:58,921 --> 00:29:00,773

319
00:29:02,220 --> 00:29:06,840
I would've wanted to try the 12-course wedding banquet if it weren't for you,

320
00:29:06,840 --> 00:29:09,360
even though I'd have to spit it out after eating it.

321
00:29:10,260 --> 00:29:14,760
If it were possible, I’d want to attend your wedding even more.

322
00:29:14,760 --> 00:29:18,080
As long as there's some liquor and roasted chicken.

323
00:29:25,060 --> 00:29:28,580
My son, go home.

324
00:29:38,640 --> 00:29:41,200
Let's depart.

325
00:29:43,540 --> 00:29:45,580
We're too close to Prince Jingyu's Mansion.

326
00:29:45,580 --> 00:29:49,080
And the person Xiao Ruofeng assigned to escort the carriage is difficult to deal with.

327
00:29:49,080 --> 00:29:52,600
If we go and take him directly, I'm afraid...

328
00:29:54,480 --> 00:29:56,920
Write to Envoy Wuxiang.

329
00:29:56,920 --> 00:30:01,100
We will stay here and observe the situation.

330
00:31:09,060 --> 00:31:12,680
The wedding yesterday was lively indeed.

331
00:31:12,680 --> 00:31:15,600
They did a great job hiding it from me.

332
00:31:15,600 --> 00:31:18,240
Yi Bu and Ruojin didn’t want me to know about it

333
00:31:18,240 --> 00:31:20,440
because they couldn’t tell what my intentions were.

334
00:31:20,440 --> 00:31:22,860
They were afraid that I might jeopardize the wedding.

335
00:31:22,860 --> 00:31:27,340
As for Ruofeng, he's the only one doing it for other people's sake.

336
00:31:27,340 --> 00:31:29,040
He did it for his brother's sake.

337
00:31:29,040 --> 00:31:31,780
He even did it for Ye Yun's sake.

338
00:31:31,780 --> 00:31:38,580
Among all my sons, some have wild ambitions, some are ruthless,

339
00:31:38,580 --> 00:31:40,960
and some are strategically brilliant.

340
00:31:40,960 --> 00:31:46,740
However, only Ruofeng is kind.

341
00:31:46,740 --> 00:31:53,090
As a ruler, I wonder if being kind is a blessing or a curse.

342
00:32:02,980 --> 00:32:07,540
Do you think I'm kind?

343
00:32:09,780 --> 00:32:11,960
Your Majesty, pardon me for speaking too much.

344
00:32:13,040 --> 00:32:15,680
Small kindness benefits individuals, while great kindness benefits the world.

345
00:32:15,680 --> 00:32:19,580
Good people practice small kindness, while a wise ruler practices great kindness.

346
00:32:19,580 --> 00:32:22,920
When there is a wise ruler, a prosperous era will be ushered in.

347
00:32:22,920 --> 00:32:26,340
However, if a good person rules the nation, the world will be plunged into chaos.

348
00:32:26,340 --> 00:32:31,730
As I don't practice great kindness, I don't pay attention to small kindness either.

349
00:32:31,730 --> 00:32:34,160
But Ruofeng,

350
00:32:36,820 --> 00:32:39,880
he's different.

351
00:32:45,300 --> 00:32:48,640
Your Majesty, Prince Qing requests an audience.

352
00:32:52,300 --> 00:32:54,900
- Summon him. 
 - Yes, Your Majesty.

353
00:32:57,680 --> 00:33:01,800
Summon Prince Qing!

354
00:33:07,600 --> 00:33:10,880
Old Second, what brings you here today?

355
00:33:10,880 --> 00:33:12,760
I'm not busy today anyway.

356
00:33:12,760 --> 00:33:17,200
Imperial Father, I can visit you every day as long as you're willing.

357
00:33:17,200 --> 00:33:19,440
You're not busy today, huh?

358
00:33:19,440 --> 00:33:23,880
But I heard that you didn't even attend Old Third's wedding.

359
00:33:30,640 --> 00:33:34,760
I didn't attend it as I was afraid I might embarrass him.

360
00:33:34,760 --> 00:33:38,500
Not only did you not attend it, but you're also saying that you might embarrass him if you do?

361
00:33:39,960 --> 00:33:42,620
Initially, I was planning to attend.

362
00:33:42,620 --> 00:33:44,640
But I heard that someone was going to steal the bride.

363
00:33:44,640 --> 00:33:47,920
It was a prince's wedding, yet crooks were trying to steal his bride.

364
00:33:47,920 --> 00:33:52,540
If I witnessed the event, I'm sure Ruojin would be embarrassed.

365
00:33:53,520 --> 00:33:57,000
Why haven't I received any news about it?

366
00:34:01,680 --> 00:34:06,060
I'm afraid someone... swept it under the rug on purpose.

367
00:34:06,860 --> 00:34:11,440
Imperial Father, they have no respect for you at all.

368
00:34:11,440 --> 00:34:13,400
That's enough.

369
00:34:13,400 --> 00:34:14,880
Tell me, then.

370
00:34:14,880 --> 00:34:19,080
Who's daring enough to sabotage the marriage that I've granted?

371
00:34:19,080 --> 00:34:21,360
Of course, it's that wretched Ye Family's Ye Yun.

372
00:34:21,360 --> 00:34:26,060
Not only did he do it himself, but he also called upon his best friend, Baili Dongjun.

373
00:34:26,060 --> 00:34:30,280
Of course, with Old Nine around, they were unable to do anything.

374
00:34:34,140 --> 00:34:36,320
Baili Dongjun?

375
00:34:42,720 --> 00:34:48,450
Are you saying that Old Nine was the one who handled it in the end?

376
00:34:48,450 --> 00:34:52,560
About that, I don't know the details either.

377
00:34:55,320 --> 00:35:00,000
The lass from the Shadow Sect was indeed betrothed to the General's Mansion.

378
00:35:00,000 --> 00:35:02,320
But that was a long time ago.

379
00:35:02,320 --> 00:35:05,640
So, they actually had such a relationship?

380
00:35:05,640 --> 00:35:07,680
- Where are they? 
 - They vanished.

381
00:35:07,680 --> 00:35:12,080
But I saw one of Marquis of Zhenxi's carriages leaving Tianqi in secret later.

382
00:35:12,080 --> 00:35:15,160
And there were two individuals in the carriage.

383
00:35:15,160 --> 00:35:19,560
Are you saying that the Marquis of Zhenxi took them away?

384
00:35:20,200 --> 00:35:22,880
It does make sense when you think about it.

385
00:35:22,880 --> 00:35:26,440
After all, the Marquis of Zhenxi was great friends with the Great General.

386
00:35:26,440 --> 00:35:28,300
They were close indeed.

387
00:35:28,300 --> 00:35:30,897
Although they've been separated by death for many years,

388
00:35:30,897 --> 00:35:34,080
he's still protecting that son of his.

389
00:35:34,080 --> 00:35:36,500
You're wrong.

390
00:35:40,640 --> 00:35:47,800
It was Baili Luochen, Ye Yu, and I who were sworn brothers together.

391
00:35:51,380 --> 00:35:53,240
Pardon me for the offense.

392
00:36:00,319 --> 00:36:04,760

393
00:36:11,980 --> 00:36:13,660
You're awake.

394
00:36:17,660 --> 00:36:20,240
- What time is it? 
 - You don't need to worry.

395
00:36:20,240 --> 00:36:23,300
You've been unconscious for two days.

396
00:36:23,300 --> 00:36:25,080
Who are you?

397
00:36:26,460 --> 00:36:28,180
I have the same surname as you, Ye.

398
00:36:28,180 --> 00:36:29,660
My name is Ye Xiaoying.

399
00:36:29,660 --> 00:36:32,920
But don't misunderstand. I'm not related to you by any means.

400
00:36:32,920 --> 00:36:36,320
I was born in an ordinary village called Ye Village.

401
00:36:36,320 --> 00:36:38,960
I grew up listening to tales of General Ye.

402
00:36:38,960 --> 00:36:40,960
I admire him a lot.

403
00:36:44,260 --> 00:36:46,360
- Who are you? 
 - Didn't I make myself clear?

404
00:36:46,360 --> 00:36:50,460
Fine. I'll be more specific. Right now, I'm a commander, leading a squad.

405
00:36:50,460 --> 00:36:53,040
It's called Ye Camp. I came up with it.

406
00:36:53,040 --> 00:36:57,220
That's right. I want my Ye Camp to be just like the legendary Ye Camp.

407
00:36:57,220 --> 00:36:59,660
We'll dominate the battlefield.

408
00:37:02,060 --> 00:37:05,780
Stop using your real energy. You'll die for real if you keep using it.

409
00:37:05,780 --> 00:37:09,020
But don't worry. My boss is wealthy.

410
00:37:09,020 --> 00:37:12,080
He fed you over ten kinds of pills and elixirs.

411
00:37:12,080 --> 00:37:15,160
You'll recover in around ten days or so.

412
00:37:15,160 --> 00:37:17,060
But I have a piece of advice.

413
00:37:17,060 --> 00:37:21,000
don't use the Immovable Lord Technique and Demon Deity Sword Techniques again.

414
00:37:22,260 --> 00:37:27,000
Why did you stop me... without killing me?

415
00:37:27,000 --> 00:37:29,640
It's because my boss is a good person.

416
00:37:30,300 --> 00:37:32,580
He just has a scumbag for a brother.

417
00:37:32,580 --> 00:37:34,400
I'll tell you this again.

418
00:37:34,400 --> 00:37:37,840
My name is Ye Xiaoying.

419
00:37:37,840 --> 00:37:42,560
Right now, I may be a nobody, but I'll be a great general in the future.

420
00:37:42,560 --> 00:37:46,000
Forget being a general. It would be a shame.

421
00:37:48,100 --> 00:37:51,400
You should just become the top martial artist in the world.

422
00:37:52,340 --> 00:37:53,940
All right, he's here.

423
00:37:53,940 --> 00:37:57,180
Take care of yourself. May we see each other again.

424
00:37:57,180 --> 00:37:59,220
Xiao Ruofeng!

425
00:38:03,020 --> 00:38:05,720
- You must hate me to the core. 
 - What do you think?

426
00:38:05,720 --> 00:38:08,720
Even if I didn't stop you, you still wouldn't have had a chance to win.

427
00:38:08,720 --> 00:38:10,820
The ending would still be the same.

428
00:38:10,820 --> 00:38:14,200
However, there would be no turning back.

429
00:38:14,200 --> 00:38:17,160
Is that your excuse?

430
00:38:25,620 --> 00:38:29,880
Do you think Tianqi City is beautiful?

431
00:38:33,720 --> 00:38:37,280
Tianqi City is known as the best city of all cities.

432
00:38:37,280 --> 00:38:40,960
It's a city that gathers all the glory and wealth of the world into one.

433
00:38:40,960 --> 00:38:47,240
However, the more beautiful something is, the more fragile it is.

434
00:38:47,240 --> 00:38:53,400
To some, it consists of 32 music houses, 64 liquor parlors,

435
00:38:53,400 --> 00:38:58,480
the legendary gambling parlor, Qianjin House, and the legendary Changyu House.

436
00:38:59,900 --> 00:39:06,720
But to me, it consists of one imperial palace, three princes' mansions,

437
00:39:06,720 --> 00:39:09,600
the Five Grand Eunuchs, the Directorate of Astronomy, Marquis of Huaiyu Mansion,

438
00:39:09,600 --> 00:39:12,120
the Six Ministries, the Grand Preceptor Mansion,

439
00:39:12,120 --> 00:39:16,120
Jinwu Guards, who patrol the city openly, and the Shadow Sect, which lurks in the dark.

440
00:39:16,120 --> 00:39:20,620
And it also consists of the Imperial Guards stationed outside the city.

441
00:39:20,620 --> 00:39:22,800
There are many forces and their relationships are complex.

442
00:39:22,800 --> 00:39:30,440
Due to that, I cannot judge an issue or event based on my preference most of the time.

443
00:39:37,220 --> 00:39:40,240
Are you going to tell me...

444
00:39:40,240 --> 00:39:43,480
that you can't do anything because you're controlled by the court?

445
00:39:48,880 --> 00:39:50,940
Why aren't you saying anything?

446
00:39:53,440 --> 00:39:55,400
Because you're right.

447
00:39:56,260 --> 00:40:00,300
I can't do anything when I'm being controlled by the court.

448
00:40:06,480 --> 00:40:08,180
I'm different from other princes.

449
00:40:08,180 --> 00:40:10,820
I loved spending time in the military camp since young.

450
00:40:10,820 --> 00:40:15,200
Back then, General Ye taught me a lot of things.

451
00:40:15,200 --> 00:40:18,580
I was on my first expedition when the tragedy befell General Ye.

452
00:40:18,580 --> 00:40:25,240
Everything had already been decided when I rushed back to Tianqi City upon hearing the news.

453
00:40:28,180 --> 00:40:29,540
I know.

454
00:40:29,540 --> 00:40:33,500
Back then, Dongjun idolized me.

455
00:40:33,500 --> 00:40:35,200
And I...

456
00:40:37,420 --> 00:40:39,520
once idolized you as well.

457
00:40:42,500 --> 00:40:47,620
Look, to the north of Beili are barbarian tribes.

458
00:40:47,620 --> 00:40:50,280
They excel at combat and are ferocious.

459
00:40:50,280 --> 00:40:52,020
South of Beili is Nanjue.

460
00:40:52,020 --> 00:40:53,940
They just achieved unification.

461
00:40:53,940 --> 00:40:56,140
They're raring to achieve greater feats.

462
00:40:56,820 --> 00:40:59,000
But Beili?

463
00:40:59,580 --> 00:41:03,380
The greatest general and his clan were executed.

464
00:41:03,380 --> 00:41:06,880
The most influential marquises left the imperial court.

465
00:41:06,880 --> 00:41:09,940
My father, the Emperor, is getting old. The princes are having an internal struggle.

466
00:41:09,940 --> 00:41:15,780
Tianqi City may look prosperous, but it's on the brink of collapsing.

467
00:41:16,340 --> 00:41:22,300
At this moment, someone has to stand up and stabilize the situation.

468
00:41:27,980 --> 00:41:32,420
You want to become... that individual?

469
00:41:32,420 --> 00:41:34,320
It's not that I wish to do so.

470
00:41:34,320 --> 00:41:37,080
It's that I have to do so.

471
00:41:38,580 --> 00:41:41,800
Our backgrounds aren't as noble as the other princes.

472
00:41:41,800 --> 00:41:44,180
We don't have influential forces backing us up.

473
00:41:44,180 --> 00:41:47,180
Therefore, we have no choice but to ally ourselves with other forces.

474
00:41:47,180 --> 00:41:51,060
For example, the Shadow Sect.

475
00:41:51,060 --> 00:41:55,420
This marriage is just an alliance between the two forces.

476
00:41:55,420 --> 00:41:58,180
Dingzhi, I wish to help you out as well.

477
00:41:58,180 --> 00:42:00,300
I wish to draw my sword and side with you as well.

478
00:42:00,300 --> 00:42:02,480
But I cannot!

479
00:42:04,300 --> 00:42:05,980
It's because

480
00:42:06,780 --> 00:42:09,100
I'm Prince Langya.

481
00:42:09,100 --> 00:42:14,300
I'm Prince Langya of the Xiao Family in Beili.

482
00:42:18,100 --> 00:42:23,740
I know. In the end, we ruined your happiness for the sake of our interests.

483
00:42:23,740 --> 00:42:27,660
I... I've let you down.

484
00:42:28,380 --> 00:42:31,970
But Dingzhi, in this world,

485
00:42:31,970 --> 00:42:38,340
who can truly live with a clear conscience?

486
00:42:41,060 --> 00:42:44,460
Ye Yun, regarding the case of General Ye, I'll give you my promise.

487
00:42:44,460 --> 00:42:46,940
I'll definitely overturn his case.

488
00:42:46,940 --> 00:42:52,640
I'll also uphold justice for the entire General's Mansion.

489
00:42:56,740 --> 00:42:59,820
So, farewell.

490
00:42:59,820 --> 00:43:06,980
From now on, I hope you can live on.

491
00:43:11,780 --> 00:43:14,190
Do you think I'll take pity on you

492
00:43:15,310 --> 00:43:18,440
